      <p begin="00:54:02.330" end="00:54:05.349">- *[Raul] Klinkt goed.*<br/>- Ja.</p>
      <p begin="00:54:05.349" end="00:54:06.271">&#9834; [muziek] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:54:06.271" end="00:54:11.306">&#9834; Sometimes a song is funky<br/>Coz you feel that way &#9834;</p>
